Generalize a vm in azure
	Pubrpose of Generalization
	1.Resets server-specific data
		-computer name
		-Security identifiers(SIDs)
		-Local Administrator/root identity
		-Device driver cache
		-Event logs
	2.Take a VM backup first,because generalization is destructive and permanent
	Managed Disks
		Disks
			a.No storage(management) required
			b.Pay for pre-allocated storage(P10=128 GB SSD VHD)
			
		Snapshots
			
